        <div class="sim-card-title">Struktur tabel — <code>satusehat_log</code> (master) &amp; <code>satusehat_log_detail</code> (attempt + audit)</div>
      </div>
      <div class="sim-subhead"><span class="sim-subhead-dot"></span>1. <code>satusehat_log</code> — satu baris per resource (status terkini)</div>
      <div class="sim-table-wrap">
        <table class="sim-table" style="min-width:580px;">
          <thead><tr><th style="width:140px;">Nama kolom</th><th style="width:100px;">Tipe data</th><th style="width:110px;">Contoh nilai</th><th>Keterangan untuk developer</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td class="sim-mono">id</td><td class="sim-mono">BIGINT AUTO</td><td class="sim-mono">1, 2, 3...</td><td class="sim-td-desc">Primary key tabel log ini sendiri — bukan dari regpas</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="sim-mono">module</td><td class="sim-mono">ENUM</td><td class="sim-mono">igd</td><td class="sim-td-desc">Diambil dari <code>regpas.modul</code> — nilai: igd, rajal, ranap</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="sim-mono">resource_type</td><td class="sim-mono">VARCHAR(50)</td><td class="sim-mono">Encounter</td><td class="sim-td-desc">Tipe FHIR: Patient, Encounter, Observation, Condition, Procedure, dll</td></tr>
            <tr class="sim-hl"><td class="sim-mono sim-info">noreg</td><td class="sim-mono">VARCHAR(20)</td><td class="sim-mono">2606060001</td><td class="sim-td-desc sim-info">Pengganti regpas_id — nomor registrasi pasien format YYMMDDNNNN. Dilebarkan ke VARCHAR(20) untuk antisipasi perubahan format. NULL hanya untuk Patient</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="sim-mono">source_table</td><td class="sim-mono">VARCHAR(50)</td><td class="sim-mono">vitalsign</td><td class="sim-td-desc">Nama tabel asal data di SIMRS — dipakai job untuk ambil data saat retry</td></tr>
            <tr class="sim-hl"><td class="sim-mono sim-info">source_id</td><td class="sim-mono">VARCHAR(12)</td><td class="sim-mono">2606060001</td><td class="sim-td-desc sim-info">ID baris di source_table. Untuk Encounter: isinya noreg juga. Untuk vitalsign: ID integer vitalsign. Tipe VARCHAR agar bisa menampung noreg maupun integer</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="sim-mono">observation_code</td><td class="sim-mono">VARCHAR(20) NULL</td><td class="sim-mono">8310-5</td><td class="sim-td-desc">Kode LOINC — hanya diisi untuk resource_type = Observation. NULL untuk resource lain</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="sim-mono">encounter_status</td><td class="sim-mono">ENUM NULL</td><td class="sim-mono">arrived</td><td class="sim-td-desc">Status fase Encounter — hanya diisi untuk resource_type = Encounter. Diganti VARCHAR → <code>ENUM('arrived','in-progress','finished','cancelled')</code> agar tidak ada typo saat insert. NULL untuk resource lain</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="sim-mono">status</td><td class="sim-mono">ENUM</td><td class="sim-mono">pending</td><td class="sim-td-desc">Status pengiriman: pending, retrying, sent, failed</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="sim-mono">ihs_id</td><td class="sim-mono">VARCHAR(100) NULL</td><td class="sim-mono">enc-igd-999</td><td class="sim-td-desc">ID dari SatuSehat setelah berhasil terkirim — diisi otomatis oleh job saat response 201/200</td></tr>
            <tr class="sim-hl"><td class="sim-mono sim-info">retry_count</td><td class="sim-mono">TINYINT</td><td class="sim-mono">0, 1, 2</td><td class="sim-td-desc sim-info">Kolom baru — hitungan retry. Di-increment tiap kali RetryService kirim ulang, jadi cek batas maksimal ("retry_count &lt; 3") tanpa perlu COUNT ke tabel detail</td></tr>
            <tr class="sim-hl"><td class="sim-mono sim-info">last_error</td><td class="sim-mono">VARCHAR(500) NULL</td><td class="sim-mono">Invalid LOINC code</td><td class="sim-td-desc sim-info">Kolom baru — ringkasan error terakhir langsung di master. Dashboard bisa tampilkan error tanpa JOIN ke <code>satusehat_log_detail</code>. NULL saat belum pernah gagal</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="sim-mono">sent_at</td><td class="sim-mono">DATETIME NULL</td><td class="sim-mono">2026-06-06 08:01</td><td class="sim-td-desc">Waktu berhasil terkirim — NULL sampai status berubah jadi sent</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="sim-mono">created_at</td><td class="sim-mono">DATETIME</td><td class="sim-mono">2026-06-06 08:00</td><td class="sim-td-desc">Waktu baris dibuat oleh Observer — otomatis diisi database</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="sim-mono">updated_at</td><td class="sim-mono">DATETIME</td><td class="sim-mono">2026-06-06 08:01</td><td class="sim-td-desc">Waktu terakhir baris ini diubah — auto update setiap kali status berubah</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <div class="sim-index-wrap">
        <div class="sim-index-title">Index yang wajib dibuat:</div>
        <div class="sim-index-list">
          INDEX idx_noreg_status (noreg, status) — untuk dashboard: filter per kunjungan + status<br>
          INDEX idx_module_status (module, status) — untuk dashboard: ringkasan per modul<br>
          INDEX idx_source (source_table, source_id) — untuk retry: cari log dari tabel sumber<br>
          INDEX idx_resource_lookup (noreg, resource_type) — untuk ambil ihs_id Encounter/Patient<br>
          INDEX idx_status_retry (status, retry_count) — index baru: RetryService query "failed AND retry_count &lt; 3"
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="sim-subhead sim-subhead--gap"><span class="sim-subhead-dot sim-subhead-dot--accent"></span>2. <code>satusehat_log_detail</code> — satu baris per attempt (request + response disimpan di sini)</div>
      <p class="sim-desc" style="margin: 8px 24px 16px;">
        Opsi yang dipakai: <b>menyimpan payload langsung di tabel detail</b> (bukan tabel terpisah). Satu
        <code>satusehat_log</code> bisa punya banyak attempt saat retry, jadi tiap attempt butuh jejak
        request/response sendiri. Relasi: <code>satusehat_log_detail.log_id → satusehat_log.id</code> (one-to-many).
      </p>
      <div class="sim-table-wrap">
        <table class="sim-table" style="min-width:600px;">
          <thead><tr><th style="width:140px;">Nama kolom</th><th style="width:120px;">Tipe data</th><th style="width:120px;">Contoh nilai</th><th>Keterangan untuk developer</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td class="sim-mono">id</td><td class="sim-mono">BIGINT AUTO</td><td class="sim-mono">1, 2, 3...</td><td class="sim-td-desc">Primary key tabel detail</td></tr>
            <tr class="sim-hl"><td class="sim-mono sim-info">log_id</td><td class="sim-mono">BIGINT FK</td><td class="sim-mono">42</td><td class="sim-td-desc sim-info">Foreign key ke <code>satusehat_log.id</code>. ON DELETE CASCADE</td></tr>
            <tr class="sim-hl"><td class="sim-mono sim-info">noreg</td><td class="sim-mono">VARCHAR(20) NULL</td><td class="sim-mono">2606060001</td><td class="sim-td-desc sim-info">Kolom baru — redundan (disalin dari <code>satusehat_log.noreg</code> saat insert) agar query "semua attempt untuk kunjungan X" cepat tanpa JOIN</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="sim-mono">attempt_no</td><td class="sim-mono">SMALLINT</td><td class="sim-mono">1, 2</td><td class="sim-td-desc">Urutan percobaan kirim. Naik tiap kali RetryService dispatch ulang</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="sim-mono">http_method</td><td class="sim-mono">VARCHAR(8)</td><td class="sim-mono">POST, PUT</td><td class="sim-td-desc">Verb HTTP yang dipakai. PUT dipakai untuk update Encounter finished</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="sim-mono">endpoint</td><td class="sim-mono">VARCHAR(255)</td><td class="sim-mono">/Observation</td><td class="sim-td-desc">Path relatif yang dipanggil. ImagingStudy memakai base URL NIDR, bukan base FHIR biasa</td></tr>
            <tr class="sim-hl"><td class="sim-mono sim-info">request_body</td><td class="sim-mono">JSON / LONGTEXT</td><td class="sim-mono">&#123;"resourceType":…&#125;</td><td class="sim-td-desc sim-info">Payload FHIR mentah yang dikirim. Pakai tipe <code>JSON</code> (MySQL 5.7+/Postgres <code>JSONB</code>) agar bisa di-query</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="sim-mono">response_status</td><td class="sim-mono">SMALLINT</td><td class="sim-mono">201, 422, 500</td><td class="sim-td-desc">HTTP status code dari response SatuSehat</td></tr>
            <tr class="sim-hl"><td class="sim-mono sim-info">response_body</td><td class="sim-mono">JSON / LONGTEXT</td><td class="sim-mono">&#123;"resourceType":…&#125;</td><td class="sim-td-desc sim-info">Body response: resource lengkap saat sukses, atau <code>OperationOutcome</code> saat error</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="sim-mono">error_message</td><td class="sim-mono">TEXT NULL</td><td class="sim-mono">Invalid LOINC code</td><td class="sim-td-desc">Ringkasan error (diambil dari <code>OperationOutcome.issue.diagnostics</code>). NULL saat sukses</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="sim-mono">duration_ms</td><td class="sim-mono">INT NULL</td><td class="sim-mono">248</td><td class="sim-td-desc">Latensi request dalam milidetik — berguna untuk monitoring performa</td></tr>
            <tr class="sim-hl"><td class="sim-mono sim-info">triggered_by</td><td class="sim-mono">VARCHAR(64)</td><td class="sim-mono">system:RetryService</td><td class="sim-td-desc sim-info">Aktor yang memicu attempt. Format <code>system:&lt;NamaJob&gt;</code> untuk job otomatis, atau <code>user:&lt;NIP/username&gt;</code> bila resend manual dari dashboard</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="sim-mono">created_at</td><td class="sim-mono">DATETIME</td><td class="sim-mono">2026-06-06 08:31</td><td class="sim-td-desc">Waktu attempt dieksekusi — otomatis diisi database</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <div class="sim-index-wrap">
        <div class="sim-index-title">Index &amp; constraint untuk <code>satusehat_log_detail</code>:</div>
        <div class="sim-index-list">
          FOREIGN KEY (log_id) REFERENCES satusehat_log(id) ON DELETE CASCADE<br>
          INDEX idx_log_attempt (log_id, attempt_no) — ambil semua attempt satu resource secara urut<br>
          INDEX idx_noreg_detail (noreg, created_at) — pengganti idx_status_created: "semua attempt untuk kunjungan X" tanpa JOIN<br>
          INDEX idx_log_created (log_id, created_at) — ambil attempt terbaru dari 1 log (ORDER BY created_at DESC)
        </div>
      </div>
